{{Infobox quest |name = Philharmonic Dust-Up |image = XC3 Challenge Battle Mode.png |description = "Demihumans of desert form musical band! But please to not get distracted by tunes. Big ones spell big danger!" |giver = [[Nopon Archsage]] |location = [[Land of Challenge (XC3)|Land of Challenge]] |difficultyCB3= 2 |rewards = 500-800 [[Noponstone]]s (Normal) }} '''Philharmonic Dust-Up''' is a Time Attack [[Challenge Battle Mode|Challenge Battle]] in {{XC3}}. It can be received from [[Nopon Archsage]] in the [[Land of Challenge (XC3)|Land of Challenge]], available as downloadable content from the second part of the Expansion Pass. Clearing this challenge with at least an A rank for the first time will unlock the Swimwear A outfit for [[Eunie]].
